summary:
Finally saw Detective Pikachu. I'm torn on my final opinion for a few reasons. 
I really enjoyed the CGI animation portrayal of...
body:
Finally saw Detective Pikachu. I’m torn on my final opinion for a few reasons.

I really enjoyed the CGI animation portrayal of all the Pokemon and the Zootopia-like city of them interacting harmoniously with humans including black market battles.

  • However on the bad side, they added an unnecessary love plot for the main character (although it didn’t take up that much of movie time). More importantly on the negative side was the ending explanation that Pikachu was really the dad all along? It completely changed the dynamic of the relationship and due to that slightly tarnished the aspect that Pikachu had become his first partner.
